title: [Mairiseth Telearat, Courtyard]
description: Verdant clusters of flora-strewn booths are scattered across the cobblestone courtyard, the medley of wares displayed atop oiled countertops and stacks of latticed baskets.  A duo of tall nielira-shaped topiaries flank the ivy-draped entryway, the jellyfish rising from spherical faerthiel bubbles awash with gilded ink.  A naefira-draped walkway looped with heartleaf-woven strands of colorful faerthiel leads back into the town proper, the illuminated blooms woven through the trellises.
